Size Matters

Featuring its small, lightweight and innovative
design, Transcend delivers the most truly portable,
clinically effective CPAP devices in the world

 

 

Power for any occasion

Because life doesn't sit still

 

 

Freedom To Sleep Anywhere

Portable CPAP therapy for the active lifestyle.

 

• Fits in carry-on (laptop bag, briefcase or overnight bag; no extra bags needed)
• Small & lightweight
• Often hard to find power outlets in hotel rooms or don't have proper adaptor
• Battery options
• Multi-plug power supply

Business Travel

Compact and lightweight,
Transcend sleep therapy devices
are FAA approved for all major
airlines and fit in carry-on bags

Go anywhere under the stars and off the power grid (power options)
Stay as long as you like (Solar battery charger)
No need to buy multiple batteries for multiple nights off the grid

Outdoor

Go anywhere under the stars and off the grid with Transcend's portable power options.

• Small & lightweight (easy to pack; doesn't take up souvenir space)
• Often hard to find power outlets in hotel rooms or cruise ships (battery options)
• Power options fit any leisure travel desire (multi-plug power supply, mobile power adaptor, batteries, solar battery charger)

Leisure Travel

Small & lightweight with an array
of power options that allow you
to travel without limits

Inflight use with or without power plugs (coach, business & first class)
Approved for inflight use

FAA approved

Transcend devices are FAA
approved, small, lightweight and
quiet. Allowing therapy inflight
with either P4 or P8 battery.

• Easy to store (small)
• No need to drain truck battery power (battery power options)
• Low power consumption (mobile power adaptor options)
• TranSync data reporting when compliance monitoring is required

Trucking

The perfect companion for truck
drivers who require clinically
effective CPAP therapy on the go

At home or on-the-go, Transcend provides the sleep
apnea therapy you need.

 

Transcend Auto™ mini CPAP

Transcend AUTO is a fully-featured APAP with EZEX pressure relief.  The Auto continually monitors your breathing to adapt to your changing therapy needs. Transcend EZEX technology provides pressure relief on exhalation for more breathing comfort.

  • Small, fully-featured APAP
  • Transcend EZEX™ pressure relief technology
  • TranSync compatible
  • Most innovative & portable APAP in the world
  • Weighs less than one pound

 

 

Transcend EZEX™ mini CPAP

Transcend EZEX is a fully-featured CPAP with EZEX technology that provides pressure relief on exhalation for more breathing comfort.

  • Small, fully-featured CPAP
  • Transcend EZEX™ pressure relief technology
  • TranSync compatible
  • Most innovative & portable CPAP in the world
  • Weighs less than one pound

 

 

Transcend® mini CPAP

Transcend mini CPAP is a fully-featured CPAP device designed for your mobile lifestyle.

  • Small, fully-featured CPAP
  • TranSync compatible
  • Most innovative & portable CPAP in the world
  • Weighs less than one pound

 

 

 

WHY TRANSCEND?

Transcend is the first portable CPAP device designed completely around user lifestyle to give CPAP users the freedom to sleep anywhere. These small, lightweight portable CPAP devices are about the size of a soda can and have portable battery options the size of a deck of cards for easy packing and toting. It’s portable CPAP therapy that’s ready for anything.
